N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 21 ยง 1275.5 - Permission to post or distribute printed matter required

State Regulations

No person shall post, distribute or display signs, advertisements, circulars, printed or written matter at the air terminal
without permission. Notes
